'We are treating this death as suspicious and are actively following up several lines of enquiry today.

'Perhaps you saw the man drop from the flat or heard a disturbance in the moments before or after he fell - please speak to officers at the scene or give us a call.'

Anyone with information should contact West Midlands Police on 101 or Crimestoppers on 0800 555 111.

